To run with the default input file (../out_p3.dat), output file (fig.png), figure title ('TITLE'), and 1-ice-category
execute:

$ python3 plot_kin1d.py 

 
To specify one of more of these, execute:

$ python3 plot_kin1d.py -i [my_input_file] -f my_fig_name.png -t 'my awesome title' -n [# ice categories]

If you forget, get help with:

$ python3 plot_1col.py -h

If -n is not specified, the default value is 1, so only the first ice category will be plotted, even if kin1d
was run with multiple categories (i.e. nCat > 1).
 

